OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1781783276
OL,3,CJim Allister defends sharing cartoon
OL,4,Cof migrants on board bus to Belfast
OL,6,FTUV leader Jim Allister has defended
OL,7,Fsharing a cartoon depicting migrants
OL,8,Ftravelling on a bus to Belfast.
OL,10,FThe post, shared on Mr Allister's
OL,11,Fsocial media channels, included the
OL,12,Fslogan 'Stop the Buses'.
OL,14,FThe image has sparked outrage from
OL,15,Fsome who claim it is "racist".
OL,17,FIt comes after violence flared in
OL,18,FNorthern Ireland following the
OL,19,Fstabbing of a man in north Belfast
OL,20,Flast Monday.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/6
