FL,414,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1781783276
OL,3,CJim Allister defends sharing cartoon
OL,4,Cof migrants on board bus to Belfast
OL,6,FWhile respecting the right to debate
OL,7,Fpolicy, some believe posting the
OL,8,Fcartoon during a time of heightened
OL,9,Ftensions was irresponsible.
OL,11,FAlliance MLA Kate Nicholl said: "At
OL,12,Fthe moment I am working with people
OL,13,Fwho right now are terrified.
OL,15,F"There are young children who are
OL,16,Fscared to go school right now for fear
OL,17,Fof racist attacks.
OL,19,F"For the TUV to put this out just adds
OL,20,Ffurther tension when it's already
OL,21,Fpalpable in the city right now.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,414,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1781783276
OL,3,CJim Allister defends sharing cartoon
OL,4,Cof migrants on board bus to Belfast
OL,6,F"At a time when we really needed
OL,7,Fproper leadership in Northern Ireland,
OL,8,Ffor leaders to bring people together,
OL,9,Fto remind us of our common humanity,
OL,10,Fof hope, of empathy and kindness the
OL,11,FTUV have chosen to descend into gutter
OL,12,Fpolitics."
OL,14,FMr Allister has defended the post.
OL,16,F"Of course it's a cartoon but it is
OL,17,Fmaking a serious point.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
