FL,414,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1781783276
OL,3,CJim Allister defends sharing cartoon
OL,4,Cof migrants on board bus to Belfast
OL,6,F"Stop the buses. Stop the buses that
OL,7,Fare bringing in illegal migrants to
OL,8,Ftake the benefit of the free housing,
OL,9,Fthe free money and all of that.
OL,11,F"Those are serious points. This
OL,12,Fgovernment and the last have failed to
OL,13,Fdo two things.
OL,15,F"It has failed to address the pull
OL,16,Ffactors and it has failed to have
OL,17,Fchecks on migrants crossing our open
OL,18,Fborder", he said.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/6
