OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1781783276
OL,3,CJim Allister defends sharing cartoon
OL,4,Cof migrants on board bus to Belfast
OL,6,FThe TUV and others argue that the
OL,7,FCommon Travel Area, which allows free
OL,8,Fmovement between the Republic and
OL,9,FNorthern Ireland, is being exploited
OL,10,Fon public transport by illegal
OL,11,Fmigrants seeking asylum in the UK.
OL,13,FOperation Gull, a multi-agency
OL,14,Ftaskforce that includes the Home
OL,15,FOffice and An Garda Siochana is
OL,16,Fcharged with tackling abuse of the
OL,17,Fsystem.
